This paper deals with the coordination of Electric Vehicles (EV) charging to regulate voltage on a residential electrical distribution feeder. This involves optimization and control techniques, which are typically studied in the sub-categories of control systems (cs.SY), game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.LG), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and cybernetics (cs.CY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
